title: The Source Presents Hip Hop Hits Volume 2 [1998] 320kbps
description:
Album Info

From Snoop Dogg's stoner self-confidence on "Still a G Thing" to Wyclef Jean's crossover moves on "Gone Till November," this collection peeks into every area of the hip-hop world. From Noreaga to Queen Pen to the late, great 2pac, what you get here amounts to a musical state-of-the-union address. And if these selections are any indication, the union is doing just fine. Feat.Dmx,Def Squad,Jayo Felony Jay Z,Ll Cool J,Master P
